</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>網購失蹤 4 年 The Game Awards 獎座，歸還得獎遊戲《Celeste》開發團隊</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/02/ebay/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=ebay</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 02 Mar 2022 06:09:32 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1088482</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>近日，美國知名直播主 Ryan B. 表示，在網絡拍賣平台買下了由資深媒體人 Geoff Keighley 所 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>近日，美國知名直播主 Ryan B. 表示，在網絡拍賣平台買下了由資深媒體人 Geoff Keighley 所創立的世界知名遊戲大獎「The Game Awards」的獎座，並在其 YouTube 頻道上分享了消息。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_70807"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OLKVU9mfBME?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>Ryan B. 指，在網上拍賣平台 eBay 發現了一個刻有 2018 年「The Game Awards 最佳獨立遊戲」《Celeste》的獎座。賣家在商品說明中表示獎座是「真品」，Ryan B.在半信半疑的情況下，最終以 375 美金不含運費的價格購入。經查證獎座上的資訊、重量、材質和盒子等細節後，確定獎盃為 TGA 官方獎盃。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1088485" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.34.46-694x372.png" alt="" width="694" height="372" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.34.46-694x372.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.34.46-1280x685.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.34.46-768x411.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.34.46-1536x822.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.34.46-2048x1097.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.34.46.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1088484" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.35.20-694x373.png" alt="" width="694" height="373" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.35.20-694x373.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.35.20-1280x689.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.35.20-768x413.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.35.20-1536x826.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.35.20-2048x1102.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-01-12.35.20.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<span class="s2"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OLKVU9mfBME">prestigelsKeyYoutube／截圖</a>）</span></p><p>隨後， Ryan 連繫並詢問遊戲《Celeste》開發團隊 Extremely OK Games 的運營經理 Heidy Motta 當初有否收到，Motta 表示當年並沒有收到獎座，懷疑是運送過程中出現意外，獎座至今失蹤約 4 年。Ryan 承諾將獎座歸還給 Extremely OK Games，開發商為表達感謝，表示會承擔拍賣與運送費用，並向他送出一隻簽名版的《蔚藍》遊戲實體版。</p><p>《Celeste》是一款於 2018 年推出的獨立遊戲，玩家必須在滿是陷阱的關卡中移動順便收集草莓，只要失誤就會直接死去重來。當時《Celeste》在各家媒體幾乎都拿下了接近滿分的評價，玩家更是指稱該遊戲有作為 GOTY 的資質，最終在 2018 年 TGA 上得到「最佳獨立遊戲」和「最具影響力遊戲」兩個獎項。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料來源</span><span class="s2">：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OLKVU9mfBME">prestigelsKeyYoutube</a></span>、<a href="https://gamerant.com/celeste-developer-missing-trophy-game-awards-winner-returned/">gamerant</a> —</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
